# Figma OAuth app client ID, needed to receive click/navigation events
# (Embed Kit 2.0) from embedded prototypes. Create an app at
# https://www.figma.com/developers/apps, add http://localhost:5173 as an
# embed origin, then copy the client ID here into a .env.local file
# (which is git-ignored) — don't commit real values to this file.
VITE_FIGMA_CLIENT_ID=
